[30;1m2748 | [0m[35m       W_hh before being fed into the ensuing cell at time step t.[0m
[30;1m2749 | [0m[35m       This flavor of RNN replaces the matrix multiplication between h_{t-1}[0m
[30;1m2750 | [0m[35m       and W_hh with a pointwise multiplication, resulting in performance[0m
[30;1m2751 | [0m[35m       gain.[0m

[30;1m98 | [0m[35m    **Paper abstract:**[0m
[30;1m99 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m100 | [0m[35m    *Increasing model size when pretraining natural language representations[0m
[30;1m101 | [0m[35m    often results in improved performance on downstream tasks. However, at some[0m
[30;1m102 | [0m[35m    point further model increases become harder due to GPU/TPU memory[0m

[30;1m22 | [0m[35mclass DocumentSimilarityRankerApproach(AnnotatorApproach, HasEnableCachingProperties):[0m
[30;1m23 | [0m[35m    """Annotator that uses LSH techniques present in Spark ML lib to execute[0m
[30;1m24 | [0m[35m    approximate nearest neighbors search on top of sentence embeddings.[0m
[30;1m25 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m26 | [0m[35m    It aims to capture the semantic meaning of a document in a dense,[0m
[30;1m27 | [0m[35m    continuous vector space and return it to the ranker search.[0m
